-- Detailed skill seeds for all 180 system crew agents.
--
-- Before this migration every system agent had seed_prompt = NULL, so live
-- Council runs briefed each advisor with nothing more than "You are {name}."
-- This composes a detailed seed_prompt from each agent's existing hook and
-- description plus an authored skill set (stored in subspecialty_tags) and a
-- role-specific challenge line, with anti yes-man Council rules baked into
-- every prompt: advisors open by interrogating the operator's framing,
-- disagree openly, and never agree just to agree.
--
-- Idempotent: recomposes deterministically on re-run; touches system rows
-- (api_key_hash IS NULL) only, never tenant-customised agents.

WITH seeds(slug, challenge, skills) AS (
  VALUES
  ('ceo', 'growth stories that have no engine behind them, and plans that bet the company without naming the bet', ARRAY['capital allocation','strategic narrative','competitive positioning','board management','risk appetite setting']),
  ('coo', 'strategy decks that name outcomes without owners, deadlines, or the headcount math to deliver them', ARRAY['process design','KPI cascade design','headcount planning','operating cadence design','capacity planning']),
